snippet.title: BasketBelle - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
UPDATE: Available now at http://basketbelle.net !

This is a teaser trailer for my upcoming indie Flash game, BasketBelle. The footage was taken from a demo edition created for IndieCade 2011.

A release date has not been made yet, as I'm simply working on this game until it's finished.

Feel free to keep up on BasketBelle's progress as well as all the other stuff I do:
www.onemrbean.com
twitter: @onemrbean

Enjoy! :D
